metadata.description:
This NFT contains 1 land plot. Click here to view these plots: https://app.gateofabyss.com/item/1. 
GOALAND NFTs are land plots in Gate of Abyss, a location-based RPG mobile game. Landowners can earn real income based on transactions that happen on their land plots, such as when players buy and sell items in shops, upgrade their weapons in blacksmiths, or brew potions in chemists.
Gate of Abyss website: https://gateofabyss.com/
